QuestData.Title: Start Taking Back
QuestData.Description: Today we make the first strike at the heart of the savage Vilebranch tribe. Show no mercy, $n; this is no longer just a spat between trolls. Every victory of the Revantusk is a victory for the Horde!$B$BThe Vilebranch headhunters and witch doctors will be the first to go. Make your strike against the lower terraces and report back to me with blood on your weapons.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 5 Vilebranch Witch Doctors and 5 Vilebranch Headhunters in Jintha'Alor.
QuestData.CompletionText: You'd better not get cold feet on me.
QuestData.RewardText: Well done, $n! Let the Vilebranch flee in terror from the sight of you!
